{"word":"G5272 - ὑπόκρισις - hypókrisis - hoop-ok'-ree-sis - Condemnation","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπόκρισις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hypókrisis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hoop-ok'-ree-sis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Condemnation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"மாயம், கபடம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. an answering; an answer"},{"paragraph":"2. the acting of a stage - player"},{"paragraph":"3. dissimulation, hypocrisy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee/5271\">G5271</a>; <i>acting under</i> a feigned part; that is, (figuratively) <i>deceit</i> (&ldquo;hypocrisy&rdquo;): - condemnation, dissimulation, hypocrisy."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4942 - συνυποκρίνομαι - synypokrínomai - soon-oo-pok-rin'-om-ahee/4942\">G4942</a>, <a href=\"#/G505 - ἀνυπόκριτος - anypókritos - an-oo-pok'-ree-tos/505\">G505</a>, <a href=\"#/G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee/5271\">G5271</a>, <a href=\"#/G5272 - ὑπόκρισις - hypókrisis - hoop-ok'-ree-sis/5272\">G5272</a>, <a href=\"#/G5273 - ὑποκριτής - hypokritḗs - hoop-ok-ree-tace'/5273\">G5273</a>"}]}